Strings is a sequence of characters.
Strings are immutable and cannot be changed.
Strings is a class but can be use like data type in.
There are two ways to create a string as follows

String str = "Bhavesh";
String a = new String("Bhavesh");
String Method:- Strings Method operate on java strings.
We can use these String Method to find the length of the string.
Can Covert lower case strings to uppercase strings etc.